      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "text": "Dynamic backup\n\nOutput: live rows in a relational DB\n\nDestination: a Postgres database —\nBaseout-hosted (D1 / Shared PG /\nDedicated PG) or your own (BYODB).\n\nUnlocks: SQL access, real-time sync,\nschema diffing in-database.",
